    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and she\u2019s still in wonderful shape and ready for a new home. It\u2019s a super reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend trip. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
