    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2017 Ford Focus RS represents a prime example of rally-bred engineering for the street. Powered by a 2.3L EcoBoost inline-four, it features a twin-scroll turbocharger and a high-performance cylinder head engineered for superior thermal resilience. The mechanical highlight is the Ford Performance All-Wheel Drive system with Dynamic Torque Vectoring, which utilizes a GKN rear drive unit to actively manage lateral grip and eliminate understeer. The suspension remains crisp with factory dual-mode dampers, while braking is handled by Brembo four-piston front calipers over ventilated rotors for minimal fade. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including recent PTU and RDU fluid services, ensuring the complex drivetrain operates at peak efficiency. A mechanically honest, high-lateral-G machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
