    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS. This example delivers linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, with a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul completed. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels, this M3 offers the quintessential analog driving experience.",
